name: Heliozoa_II
description:
Heliozoa_II is part of the Micrographia series that takes inspiration from the early explorers of the microscopic world. These artworks have been crafted with thoughtful insight and tender loving care. On a technical level, they mix home-brewed generative systems with hand-drawn images using Processing and GANs. 

Size : 4571x6029px PNG [bitmap image]
